title: Not selling but Seeking Honest Feedback on My Unique Pet ID Tag Prototype!
selftext:
[https://imgur.com/a/TrxQqt7](https://imgur.com/a/TrxQqt7)

I'm super excited to share my latest project with all of you - a unique pet ID tag that I've been working on. As a pet owner myself, I understand the importance of ensuring our furry friends' safety and well-being. That's why I've put my heart and soul into designing this unique pet ID tag. But before I move forward with manufacturing, I would greatly appreciate your valuable feedback and suggestions.

*Please take a moment to check out the attached images of the prototype. Your valuable feedback will help refine the product and make it even better. Additionally, I would like to know what price range you would consider reasonable for a pet ID tag like this.*
